channel.title: Model in game is invisible and wasnt before? whats wrong?
channel.description: ok so i made a skillcape of my own and added it into the game without triangulating it in metasequoia and it worked just fine when i put it on. I went back, triangulated it, and now it turns me invisible when i put it on, whats wrong?
